snippet.title: -Upperz- Kickstarter Video
snippet.description:
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/2140469607/upperz-a-fast-paced-platform-hell

Here you can get access to a lot of dope stuff :

-The Game upon release
-A Closed Beta access to see the glitches up close and play with the creation tools
-Physical Rewards, Stickers, Badges and a Vinyl Figure
-A Co-Destroyer role and privileges on Discord along with the opportunity to Co-Design a Hazard, an Enemy, a Titan, your own Super Ability or even a complete Level!
